summary: The California FAIR Plan Association is a member of the California Insurance Association. The association provides insurance for homeowners, renters and businesses in California. The California Earthquake Authority (CEA) policy is canceled if a payment is not made by the payment due date. If a check is not honored, the policy will cancel for non-payment.
